# Library and Utility Files Guide

The [`src/lib/`](mdc:src/lib) directory contains utility and helper functions used throughout the project:

- [`askForTag.ts`](mdc:src/lib/askForTag.ts): Utility for prompting the user to select a tag.
- [`loadEnv.ts`](mdc:src/lib/loadEnv.ts): Loads environment variables.
- [`validateLicense.ts`](mdc:src/lib/validateLicense.ts): Validates the license key.
- [`machineId.ts`](mdc:src/lib/machineId.ts): Retrieves the machine ID.
- [`transformSourceFileWithVisitor.ts`](mdc:src/lib/transformSourceFileWithVisitor.ts): Applies a visitor to transform a source file.
- [`findAndOperateOnNode.ts`](mdc:src/lib/findAndOperateOnNode.ts): Finds and operates on AST nodes.
- [`isElement.ts`](mdc:src/lib/isElement.ts): Checks if a node is an element.
- [`printNode.ts`](mdc:src/lib/printNode.ts): Prints an AST node.
- [`createConditionalExpression.ts`](mdc:src/lib/createConditionalExpression.ts): Creates a conditional expression node.
- [`createAmpersandExpression.ts`](mdc:src/lib/createAmpersandExpression.ts): Creates an ampersand expression node.
- [`getSourceFile.ts`](mdc:src/lib/getSourceFile.ts): Loads a TypeScript source file.
- [`wrap-creator.ts`](mdc:src/lib/wrap-creator.ts): Utility for creating wrapper nodes.
- [`createTreeWithParentKey.ts`](mdc:src/lib/createTreeWithParentKey.ts): Creates a tree structure with parent keys.
- [`visitor.ts`](mdc:src/lib/visitor.ts): Visitor pattern implementation for AST traversal.
- [`create-forward.ts`](mdc:src/lib/create-forward.ts): Creates a forward reference node.
- [`create-import-forwardRef.ts`](mdc:src/lib/create-import-forwardRef.ts): Creates an import for React's forwardRef.
